ol but gave up the sport for a time during his senior year due to \\\"mental demons\\\".\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1998, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacksonville_Jaguars\", \"score\": 0.9923023568103753, \"rank\": 0.0077554199271176825, \"text\": \"Jacksonville\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacksonville_Jaguars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacksonville_Jaguars\"}, {\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators\", \"score\": 0.98705524564361, \"rank\": 0.012778027238333283, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a swimming family\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"prominence\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"a high school star\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"his senior year\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"mental demons\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A devout Christian, his faith helped steer him back of the water, with his favourite passage Bible passage inspiring the tattoo of an eagle that drapes his left shoulder.\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his faith\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"his favourite passage\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"Bible passage\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"an eagle\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2330}, 